{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji30.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给戴毓本的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给戴毓本的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1951年3月11日）毓本同志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临行一信，到兴城一信，均已收到。达到你所愿望的工作岗位，为你庆贺。已与习梅兄见面，谈了许多乡情。他不久可进学校。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺祝健进！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三月十一日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]戴毓本，杨开慧在湖南长沙福湘女校、岳云中学读书时的同学，五四运动后曾在毛泽东创办的自修大学学习。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[2]习梅，即彭习梅，戴毓本的丈夫。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1951,"month":3,"day":11}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":160,"page_end":160},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}